
sequenceDiagram

    participant Browser
    participant Server

    Browser->>Browser: Push the new note and call redrawNotes() to update the DOM

    Note right of Browser: After local update, send the note to the server

    Browser->>Server: POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa\nContent-Type: application/json, Body: JSON (content, date)
    activate Server
    Server-->>Server: Saves the note in memory
    Server-->>Browser: 201 Created
    deactivate Server

    Note right of Browser: The server does not ask for a redirect, the browser stays on the same page, and it sends no further HTTP requests
